  <br />
  <ul>
  <li>      Facts and Honesty</li>
  <li>      Freedom (with Responsibility)</li>
  <li>      Family and Community</li>
  <li>      Fairness and Equality</li>
  <li>      Opportunity and Financial Security</li>
  <li>      Sustainability and Stewardship</li>
  <li>      Participatory Democracy</li>
  <li>      Hard work, Creativity, and Good Judgment</li>
  <li>      Diversity, Pluralism and Excellence</li>
  <li>      Peace and Civility</li>
  </ul>
